These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-1::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  scientist, paramedic, nurse, bartender
4 different pets are kept: cat, ferret, lizard, turtle
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, oliveros, blend, alhambra
1. the blend-smoker is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
2. the alhambra-smoker is the owner of the cat##1
3. the nurse is on the far left##1
4. the scientist is on the far right##1
5. the owner of the ferret is between the blend-smoker and the paramedic##2
6. the oliveros-smoker is the owner of the lizard##1
7. the owner of the cat is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Job        | nurse | bartender  | paramedic | scientist  |
| Pet         | turtle    | ferret  | cat       | lizard     |
| Cigar   | blend     | tiparillo | alhambra       | oliveros |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-2::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, disco, dubstep, electronic
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, sports, superhero, zombie
4 different pets are kept: goat, rat, cat, hamster
1. the fan of disco is on the far left##1
2. the owner of the goat is on the right of the fan of funk##1
3. the owner of the rat is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the hamster is between the person watching zombie movies and the fan of electronic##2
5. the person watching zombie movies is the owner of the rat##1
6. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
7. the person watching superhero movies is the owner of the cat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |      4       |
| Music-Genre         | disco | funk    | electronic  | dubstep |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie  | fantasy  | sports   | superhero    |
| Pet         | rat | hamster | goat | cat      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-3::.
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, turtle, goat, frog
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, cooking, gardening, photography
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, swimming, ice-hockey, biathlon
1. the person who's sport is swimming is between the person who's sport is biathlon and the owner of the turtle##2
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
4. the owner of the goat is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far left##1
6. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
7. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Pet      | turtle | frog         | chinchilla   | goat    |
| Hobby         | cooking | photography | collecting | gardening |
| Sport   | ice-hockey   | swimming        | biathlon      | skateboarding   |

