.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-4::.
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, apple, radish, broccoli
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, fanta, hot-chocolate, iced-tea
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, car, scooter, ship
1. the person driving the scooter is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the bus is between the person driving the ship and the person eating broccoli##2
3. the person eating radish is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
4. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
5. the person eating radish is on the right of the person eating grapefruit##1
6. the person driving the ship is between the person drinking mirinda and the person driving the car##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |   4    |
| Food   | broccoli        | apple   | grapefruit | radish |
| Beverage         | hot-chocolate | mirinda | fanta    | iced-tea |
| Transport     | scooter       | bus     | ship       | car    |

