.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-5::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, fonseca, bongani, siglo
There are 4 different favourite colors: orange, blood-red, fuchsia, lilac
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, cricket, golf, handball
1. the person who's sport is handball is between the pall-mall-smoker and the fonseca-smoker##2
2. the person who's sport is handball is the siglo-smoker##1
3. the person who likes fuchsia is on the far right##1
4. the fonseca-smoker is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
5. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
6. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
7. the person who's sport is handball is between the person who's sport is golf and the person who likes orange##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |      3      |     4      |
| Cigar   | pall-mall | siglo      | fonseca       | bongani   |
| Color      | orange   | blood-red  | lilac | fuchsia     |
| Sport      | cricket     | handball | golf        | basketball |

