.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-6::.
4 different pets are kept: goat, goldfish, turtle, mouse
There are 4 different favourite colors: ivory, lavender, azure, apricot
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, rowing, soccer, swimming
1. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
2. the owner of the goat is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
3. the owner of the goat is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
4. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
5. the person who likes ivory is between the person who likes apricot and the person who's sport is soccer##2
6. the owner of the goldfish is between the owner of the goat and the owner of the turtle##2
7. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person who likes azure##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Pet    | turtle | goldfish  | goat | mouse      |
| Color   | azure  | apricot  | ivory | lavender |
| Sport   | swimming | ice-hockey | rowing | soccer     |

