.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-7::.
4 different games are played: whist, monopoly, chess, snooker
City: liverpool, san-francisco, prague, venice
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, cycling, handball, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
2. the person who's sport is handball is the person traveling to liverpool##1
3. the person traveling to prague is on the far left##1
4. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1
5. the person playing chess is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
6. the person playing monopoly is between the person traveling to san-francisco and the person traveling to prague##2
7. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Game          | chess  | monopoly    | snooker | whist  |
| City   | prague | venice       | san-francisco        | liverpool    |
| Sport         | cycling | badminton | volleyball  | handball |

