2. the person who's sport is sailing is between the journalist and the person who's hobby is camping##2
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the designer##1
4. the designer is on the right of the dancer##1
5. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
6. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | sudoku  | camping | cooking | board-games |
| Sport   | parkour  | swimming | sailing   | cricket         |
| Job           | dancer | designer  | paramedic   | journalist      |

