2. the pilot is the person driving the trike##1
3. the fan of house is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
4. the security-guard is the person driving the subway##1
5. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the train##1
6. the security-guard is on the far right##1
7. the pilot is between the fan of salsa and the writer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Transport          | train  | trike    | boat | subway       |
| Job         | musician | pilot | writer  | security-guard |
| Music-Genre   | salsa   | techno      | house  | ambient     |

