4. the art-deco house is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1
5. the person driving the motorbike is on the far right##1
6. the art-deco house is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1
7. the ranch-style house is the person driving the skateboard##1
8. the craftsman house is the person eating pomegranate##1

.:: Answer ::.
