1. the nigerian is the person eating grapes##1
2. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
3. the argentine is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1
4. the person eating pomegranate is between the nigerian and the italian##2
5. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person eating orange##1
6. the owner of the mouse is between the person eating grapes and the owner of the cat##2
7. the argentine is the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Food      | cranberry | pomegranate | grapes     | orange   |
| Nationality   | italian | argentine        | nigerian  | pakistani  |
| Pet           | cat      | mouse         | hedgehog | horse |

