.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-20::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, pall-mall, baccarat, oliveros
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, april, october, july
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, jet-ski, motorbike, skateboard
1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far left##1
2. the blend-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
3. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
4. the baccarat-smoker is on the far right##1
5. the person driving the skateboard is the person who's birthday is in july##1
6. the person who's birthday is in april is between the oliveros-smoker and the person driving the motorbike##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Cigar        | oliveros | pall-mall | blend | baccarat |
| Birthday         | august       | april     | october   | july   |
| Transport   | helicopter | jet-ski | motorbike | skateboard |

 